title: Two Former Anamosa Prison Correctional Officers Charged with Federal Extortion and Firearms Offenses (United States ...
text: ( Source : United States Attorney's Office for the Northern District of Iowa ) CEDAR RAPIDS - Two former Anamosa State Penitentiary correctional officers have been charged with federal offenses, while two others will be charged in state court.
